title: Print, "The Wreck of the "Atlantic" -  Cast up by the Sea", April 26, 1873
medium: Wood engraving printed in black ink on paper
provenance: Gift of Mrs. Cora E. Wilson
description: Horizontal view of rocky seacoast with boulders, with the figure of a woman in nightdress lying full length in the foreground, while beyond her, looking downward, is a man with a boathook, and in distance, at right, are a point of land with figures and foundered steamship.

tombstone.epitaph:
Print, "The Wreck of the "Atlantic" -  Cast up by the Sea", April 26, 1873.
April 26, 1873. Wood engraving printed in black ink on paper. Gift of Cora Wilson. 1939-70-3.
